query: Can I get AI to transcribe a video?
response_text: Yes. AI can transcribe a video by extracting the audio and converting it to text. Some options:  Online tools/services: Otter.ai, Rev, Sonix, Descript, Trint.  Video platforms: YouTube auto-captions (can be downloaded).  Local/programmable solutions: Use Whisper (by OpenAI) or similar speech-to-text models.  Do you want it done automatically for you, or instructions to do it yourself?
